You’ve already shown your skills in developing this mockup in HTML/CSS. Now let’s go even further and develop it using React. 

Additional level: 

Demonstrate your understanding of fundamental React concepts by developing the structural skeleton (template) of a website. Focus on component organization, layout, and basic navigation. Content and styling are not required at this stage.

Requirements:

Component Hierarchy:

    Break down the website into logical, reusable components.
    Consider a typical structure):
        App (main container)
            Header
            MainContent
                Sidebar 
                ContentArea 
            Footer
